descriptionHtml:
I made this mod for personal use and desided to share it hope you guys like it.
This mod adds a fully usable blacksmith shop outside breezehome and a outside Tikki bar on top the roof and also adds frount and side porch. Out side is a miniture arena gambling game that I couldn\'t get to work maybe someone else can do that? 
Added a fireplace in the master bedroom and extended it a little. 
All doors and Navmesh is follower friendly also there are alot of idle animations for you or your followers to do.
Added a wood choping block out back.
author: Sibastion
